take a interest in you?

272
00:20:21,355 --> 00:20:23,991
[stutters] A double take?

273
00:20:24,056 --> 00:20:25,258
[chuckles]

274
00:20:26,158 --> 00:20:27,661
Just always thought...

275
00:20:27,728 --> 00:20:31,732
You just thought
some people are creepy.

276
00:20:31,798 --> 00:20:36,770
It's better if we all
steer clear of one another.

277
00:20:37,971 --> 00:20:39,706
We're dangerous to non-Eaters,

278
00:20:39,773 --> 00:20:44,711
but we can hurt
one another just as bad.

279
00:20:44,778 --> 00:20:47,481
I hope you're
hearing me on this.

280
00:20:48,281 --> 00:20:49,416
[thunder rumbling]

281
00:20:50,717 --> 00:20:52,218
You sound like my dad.

282
00:20:52,285 --> 00:20:54,655
Your daddy find out about you?

283
00:20:59,993 --> 00:21:01,193
What about you?

284
00:21:02,729 --> 00:21:05,766
