But you came looking for me.

286
00:21:09,101 --> 00:21:10,604
[chuckling]

287
00:21:10,671 --> 00:21:12,171
Smart.

288
00:21:13,473 --> 00:21:17,544
When I saw you're just
a girl on your own,

289
00:21:19,613 --> 00:21:20,547
I thought...

290
00:21:23,149 --> 00:21:24,785
you might be hungry.

291
00:21:27,621 --> 00:21:28,622
For hens?

292
00:21:30,289 --> 00:21:32,359
[breathing heavily]

293
00:21:35,161 --> 00:21:36,630
No.

294
00:21:56,683 --> 00:21:57,751
Who lives here?

295
00:21:59,886 --> 00:22:01,421
Well, go and look.

296
00:22:11,331 --> 00:22:13,367
