Hey, don't talk to her
like that!

448
00:33:26,873 --> 00:33:28,241
Hey!

449
00:33:28,309 --> 00:33:29,809
You're out of control, buddy.

450
00:33:31,844 --> 00:33:33,580
You with the store or somethin'?

