462
00:34:21,428 --> 00:34:23,464
- [breathing heavily]
- [pensive music playing]

463
00:34:24,365 --> 00:34:25,366
[sniffling]

464
00:34:36,810 --> 00:34:38,878
[squelching]

465
00:34:54,260 --> 00:34:56,530
He's over in there, like,
400 yards if you wanna...

