I didn't know I could do that.

468
00:35:08,308 --> 00:35:10,611
I'm, uh, going to Minnesota.

469
00:35:10,677 --> 00:35:14,314
I got dumped here by a ride.
I just stole dinner.

470
00:35:14,381 --> 00:35:15,649
It was all I could think to do.

471
00:35:16,884 --> 00:35:18,117
You're not local either,
I guess.

472
00:35:18,184 --> 00:35:19,319
Why does that matter?

473
00:35:22,523 --> 00:35:24,924
That was nice what you did
for that mom in there.

474
00:35:27,694 --> 00:35:29,061
