many others.

479
00:35:39,105 --> 00:35:40,273
Sort of glad not to.

480
00:35:40,340 --> 00:35:42,141
[Maren] Yeah, I get it.

481
00:35:42,208 --> 00:35:43,444
[boy] I'm just saying
I'm not an asshole.

482
00:35:45,879 --> 00:35:48,615
