505
00:37:14,267 --> 00:37:16,303
- [sighs]
- I'm new at this.

506
00:37:16,370 --> 00:37:18,070
No one our age is new at this.

507
00:37:18,137 --> 00:37:20,172
Well, I'm new at remembering it.

508
00:37:21,140 --> 00:37:23,175
At all.

509
00:37:23,242 --> 00:37:26,245
Look, I won't try to mess
with you. I promise.

510
00:37:26,313 --> 00:37:27,748
I don't wanna hurt anybody.

